		<title>More deals, less cash: Africa’s exit problem</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/04/06/more-deals-less-cash-africas-exit-problem/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Muktar Oladunmade]]></dc:creator>
