					<description><![CDATA[Cet article est aussi disponible en français First published 05 April, 2026 More deals, less cash: Africa’s exit problem Image: Geekwire There is a saying you have probably heard since childhood: an apple a day keeps the doctor away. Applied to Africa’s technology ecosystem, the “apple” is the exit, an acquisition, IPO, or liquidity event [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
